</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udordaineq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dordaineq</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t d00d!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(12/31/01 7:36:23 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.starwars.com/episode-vi/classic/2001/02/img/chard3_52_sm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Naggy raid on dec 30 forced to be cancelled</span><hr size=1> cant see how this was stolen.  If your raid is for friday and naggy is up on tuesday.  He is a free for all till then.  Just because you post it dosent mean he sits their till you can kill him.  Emergency patches will happen and cause your raid to be canceled so live with it.  Flameing somebody about stealing a legal mob is wrong.<br>
<br>
<br>
Dordain<br>
<br>
<br>
